   "source": [
    "import proplot as plt"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 600x368.909 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "image/png": {
       "height": 361,
       "width": 600
      }
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "colors = [\"#348ABD\", \"#A60628\"]\n",
    "prior = [1 / 21.0, 20 / 21.0]\n",
    "posterior = [0.087, 1 - 0.087]\n",
    "fig, ax = plt.subplots(aspect=(3.5, 2), width=6)\n",
    "ax.bar(\n",
    "    [0, 0.7],\n",
    "    prior,\n",
    "    alpha=0.7,\n",
    "    width=0.25,\n",
    "    color=colors[0],\n",
    "    label='prior distribution',\n",
    "    lw='3',\n",
    "    edgecolor=colors[0],\n",
    ")\n",
    "ax.bar(\n",
    "    [0 + 0.25, 0.7 + 0.25],\n",
    "    posterior,\n",
    "    alpha=0.7,\n",
    "    width=0.25,\n",
    "    color=colors[1],\n",
    "    label='posterior distribution',\n",
    "    lw='3',\n",
    "    edgecolor=colors[1],\n",
    ")\n",
    "ax.legend(loc='best')\n",
    "ax.format(\n",
    "    xticks=[0.15, 0.80],\n",
    "    xticklabels=[\"Librarian\", \"Farmer\"],\n",
    "    title=\"Prior and posterior probabilities of Steve's occupation\",\n",
    "    ylabel='Probability',\n",
    "    grid=True,\n",
    ");"
   ]
  },
